plot: John Oliver analyzes Donald Trump's re-election as the US President. He explores potential reasons behind the win, discusses what may happen during Trump's second term.

John Oliver discusses last week's biggest event: Donald Trump's second election win. He tries to breakdown the reasons that may lie behind his re-election but admitting that it is too early to be sure of the definite reasons. He talks about what might be waiting next for the 2nd presidency. Finally, he talks about what to do next till Trump takes the charge.—Niaz Islam Arif
